A '''holodocumentarian''' was an individual who created [[Holodocumentary|holodocumentaries]].

[[Wolam Tser]], a famous holodocumentarian, was responsible for narrating the [[Battle of Borleias (holodocumentary)|Battle of Borleias]] documentary, filmed by his partner, [[Tam Elgrin]].

